{"tid":2091803,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"過緊廢青生活? 成日都唔知有乜好做?   與其無所事事 不如打Twitter戰事","createTime":"2020-07-03T01:09:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T09:07:04.000Z","uid":203685,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a6311596d9548b9cb9af8bf41855adcc8e2ea079","tid":2091803,"uid":203685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T01:09:50.000Z","msg":"如果你。。。<br />\n放緊暑假好悶 想做d有意義既事<br />\n或者<br />\n想幫中共喺國際間撥火水<br />\n又或者<br />\n想見到外國制裁中共 等支爆嘅<br />\n<br />\n機會黎啦 <span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">只要每日用5分鐘 去TwitterHelpBot做一做任務 㩒like同埋retweet 就ok啦</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講真 可能只係搭一程車嘅時間 或者只係咁瞓前㩒5分鐘 你已經可以為香港爭取到更多國際關注啦 咁簡單既事 你唔係唔做掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">快d入下面條link去做任務</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=YQ8W%2FXaIcJ33D6vU0aBSBHfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=c58b3ab5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n<br />\nd 任務更新得幾快架 如果可以 就1日做2次啦 早晚各1次<br />\n<br />\n如果成日懶左 或者唔記得左做任務既話 可以試下揾d朋友互相督促住大家 當建立左習慣之後 就自然每日都會記得做架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7205d163e8d3b238af9db8e0e993955fc24375eb","tid":2091803,"uid":203685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T01:10:19.000Z","msg":"快d做任務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />